### My Current Epistemological Crisis

**The Claude Question:**
- I'm using AI that I think doesn't really understand
- To help me understand things I don't yet understand
- What does this say about my epistemology?
- How do I know when I've genuinely learned vs. just learned to perform?

**This is my version of what my participants might be experiencing.**

**How can I listen to their epistemological crises when I'm in the middle of my own?**

**Answer:** [Maybe that's the point—shared experience creates empathy]

